    {
      "id": "q9",
      "year": 110,
      "text": "若 log₂x + log₂(x-2) = 3，則 x 之值為何？",
      "options": [
        "(A) 2",
        "(B) 4",
        "(C) 6",
        "(D) 8"
      ],
      "answer": "B",
      "explanation": "解析：log₂[x(x-2)] = 3，x(x-2) = 8，x²-2x-8=0，(x-4)(x+2)=0。因真數>0，x>2，故 x=4，選(B)。",
      "tags": [
        "指數與對數函數"
      ]
    },
